  • OS: Windows 10
  • Processor: 4 core Intel or AMD
  • Memory: 8 GB RAM
  • Graphics: GTX 760 or R9 280
  • DirectX: Version 11
  • Network: Broadband Internet connection
  • Storage: 3 GB available space
  • Additional Notes: Headset and Microphone needed for Voice Chat
